title: [CRASH] <Crashed when search vector index,>
body:
Notice!
- If a Redis module was involved, please open an issue in the module's repo instead!
- If you're using docker on Apple M1, please make sure the image you're using was compiled for ARM!
redis docker image version: redis/redis-stack-server:latest

redis module:
daemonize no
loadmodule /opt/redis-stack/lib/redisearch.so
loadmodule /opt/redis-stack/lib/redisgraph.so
loadmodule /opt/redis-stack/lib/redistimeseries.so
loadmodule /opt/redis-stack/lib/rejson.so
loadmodule /opt/redis-stack/lib/redisbloom.so

using docker on centos 7.8
redis crashed when run vector index query on  chatgpt-retrieval-plugin, error details on https://github.com/openai/chatgpt-retrieval-plugin/issues/265
